    1/31/2006
        - Fix conditions for add_account_now in check_account_data.php
        - Change perm_type to perms_type in users.php (typo)
    1/26/2006
        - Add new configuration option $mysql_socket.  If set to '', the 
          system default is used.
        - Update copyright dates
        - Added canCreate/Edit/DeleteDefaultRecords functions to permissions.php
        - Move checks for isMyGroup into the top index.php file so it's only done once
        - Fix fail variable typos in users.php
    11/30/2005
        - Re-enabled basic log viewing
        - Use permissions object for checking restrictions in records.php
        - Update users.php to use pagination.php
        - Improvements to users.php permissions support
    11/23/2005
        - Update Smarty to 2.6.10
    11/18/2005
        - Use permissions object for checking domain restrictions in domains.php
        - Add canDeleteDomains() to permissions, update README.permissions
        - Move sorting code from records and domains into functions
        - Move pagination code from records.php and domains.php to
          new pagination.php
        - Maintain domain/record mode, as well as domain and record_id in
          menu expansion URLs
        - Update TODO
    11/2/2005
        - Create initial group_permissions for VegaDNS group
