* 1.1.0 2/9/2005
    - Bill Shupp (hostmaster@shupp.org)
        - Add GPL for copy of GPL License.  Update COPYING to reflect multiple
          licenses now in use.
        - Update CREDITS, UPGRADE
        - Set error_reporting(E_ALL) as recommended by ADODB
        - Switched to ADODB for multiple database support.  Only MySQL is being
          tested at this time.  (see http://adodb.sf.net)
        - Make IPv6 support optional since it requires patches to djbdns and 
          ucspi
    - Logan Michels (logan@stfunoob.com)
        - Add IPv6 support
    - Darrel O'pry (dopry@thing.net)
        - Add SRV support

