* 0.9.9 12/4/2005
    - Bill Shupp (hostmaster@shupp.org)
        - Update Smarty to 2.6.7
        - remove src link in md5upgrade directory.  Use ini_set() instead
        - update string escapes in authenticate_user() for mysql queries
          - tnx Darrel O'pry
